videos.description: DB Blaise Taylor intercepted a Brandon Duncan pass over the middle inside the redzone.
videos.headline: Arkansas St. INT stops early Arkansas-Pine Bluff momentum

videos.description: Christian Booker catches the pass over the middle and scores a 37-yard TD touchdown.
videos.headline: Red Wolves QB Hansen connects on quick slant for TD

videos.description: Justice Hansen's play action fake leaves TE Blake Mack wide open for a three-yard TD catch.
videos.headline: Hansen fools defense, throws easy TD

videos.description: Red Wolves RB Warren Wand takes the hand off and scampers 12 yards to the end zone.
videos.headline: Wand runs free for TD

videos.description: Arkansas St. QB Justice Hansen connects with  Justin McInnis who runs all the way across the field for a 73-yard TD.
videos.headline: Hansen throws TD strike to McInnis

videos.description: Arkansas St. WR Omar Bayless runs a go route and catches a 23-yard TD.
videos.headline: Bayless outruns secondary for TD

videos.description: Arkansas St. QB Logan Bonner fools the Golden Lions' defense with a play-action fake and hits an open Christian Booker for his second score.
videos.headline: Play-action frees Booker for TD
